author: Muhammad Zulhusni
description:
Huawei Cloud has rolled out Pangu Models 5.5 at the Huawei Developer Conference 2025, introducing a new round of updates focused on helping businesses solve real-world problems with AI. The latest version includes upgrades in five key areas: natural language processing (NLP), computer vision (CV), multimodal modelling, prediction, and scientific computing.
